              <img src="/images/about/experiental.jpg" alt="sidhhantha intellectual school" class="" >
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 cont">
              <h5>Experiential Learning for All Subjects</h5>
              <p>Experiential learning is at the heart of our teaching methodology. We believe that students learn best when they are actively engaged in the learning process. Whether it's history, science, mathematics, or any other subject, our teachers are dedicated to creating immersive and interactive learning experiences. This approach not only enhances academic understanding but also nurtures critical thinking, problem-solving, and creativity.</p>
          </div>
      </div> 
  </div>
    
 

    <div class="right-image">
      <div class="row gy-4">
          <div class="col-lg-5">
              
              <h5>Innovative Teaching Methods</h5>
              <p>Our teachers are passionate educators who are constantly innovating new methods to deliver academic content effectively. We understand that every student is unique, and one-size-fits-all teaching methods may not be suitable. Our educators employ diverse teaching strategies to cater to the individual learning styles and needs of our students, ensuring that no one is left behind.</p> 
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 r3">
